### 人设卡API测试

### 1. 获取公开人设卡列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/public
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 获取单个人设卡详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/public/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 用户注册（用于获取token）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. 用户登录（获取token）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 5. 上传人设卡（需要token）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "测试角色",
  "description": "这是一个测试角色",
  "content": "角色详细内容...",
  "category": "测试分类",
  "tags": ["测试", "角色"],
  "visibility": "public"
}

### 6. 获取用户自己的人设卡列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/my
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. 更新人设卡（需要token）
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "更新后的角色名",
  "description": "更新后的描述"
}

### 8. 删除人设卡（需要token）
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 管理员测试

### 9. 管理员获取人设卡列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/characters
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. 管理员获取待审核人设卡
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/characters/pending
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. 管理员审核人设卡
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/characters/1/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "approved",
  "reviewNotes": "审核通过，角色设定很有趣"
}

### 12. 管理员删除人设卡
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/characters/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. 获取人设卡统计
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/stats
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. 获取分类列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. 获取标签云
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/character/tags
Content-Type: application/json